IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SIGNAL-EXITS-LOOP.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(30).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE "MISSING-TARGET" TO TARGET-FIELD
SIGNAL HANDLER ON ERROR
LOOP
    DISPLAY "LOOP BEFORE SIGNAL FAILURE"
    GO TO TARGET-FIELD
    DISPLAY "LOOP AFTER FAILURE"
END.

HANDLER.
DISPLAY "LOOP SIGNAL HANDLER"
STOP.
